572
00:41:18,533 --> 00:41:20,167
Aduh Buyung.

573
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:24,500
Anda sama sekali tidak berubah, Pak.

574
00:41:31,833 --> 00:41:35,300
Park Dae Ho muda yang kukenal

575
